Thanks to my partner @pacificobeer for putting together this piece on how I prepare for the Olympics while staying balanced and happy in my day to day life...

What’s your life philosophy for working towards goals and maintaining your overall wellbeing? 💙💙💙

#For21+ 
#jafreespirit 
#jalivingthedream

node.text:
Life is meant to be lived to its fullest potential! In order to do so, I want to feel my best – Physically, mentally and spiritually! ✨ Thankful to be a part of this all natural CBD brand made right here in the USA! Take a look at the first athlete announcements with more to come soon–  Follow @justlive and visit the link in my bio 💙 @alexmorgan13 @klaythompson @prod @travispastrana @alexmidler @alecmajerus @ishodwair @mannysantiago @atibaphoto  @sagekotsenburg @johncollinson @camzink #justlive #athletefounded #naturegrounded
 #jafreespirit

node.text:
Words can’t express how heart aching this caldor fire is…. 💔

My dad at our family home in Meyers “ Retired Firefighter Joey Anderson in SLT is waiting out the fire at his home. A FF came by and asked how he’s holding up. He said fine as he bursted into tears. “Even in my life’s work, it’s different when it is close to home.” My dad has been in this house for forty years and I can’t imagine what he’s going through… Sending love and prayers to everyone effected 🙏
